criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  AYA is 15-29 year old with a history of a malignant cancer diagnosis;

          -  Completed cancer treatment and are currently in remission or receiving cancer
             survivorship care;

          -  Seen for follow-up oncology care at CHOP or Penn;

          -  For AYA less than 18 years old, must have a caregiver to provide informed consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Cognitive impairments that would limit AYA ability to independently care for health as
             determined by the medical team.

          -  Absence of the inclusion criteria
